{"tid":374170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次打風保險公司仲唔仆街？同大家講下今次保險要賠乜","createTime":"2017-08-25T14:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T08:10:03.000Z","uid":120655,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34591c301378ac3051639464a0a7c9d838a7a2b4","tid":374170,"uid":120655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">車保-杏花邨停車場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都知車保有分三保同全保，如果買左三保就一定唔洗諗啦，唔會有得賠<br />\n<br />\n但最多人想知係 全保 到底賠唔賠？<br />\n<br />\n車保唔係不保天災咩？八號風球下唔係唔賠咩？<br />\n<br />\n其實好多巴打都有留意有部分車保有八號風球下既不保事項，係無錯既<br />\n<br />\n不過八號風球下行駛發生既事故先係唔賠 換句話說<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">杏花邨停車場d車 並無揸出去</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以係<strong><strong><ins>受保</ins></strong></strong>既</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當然保險公司有權可以向停車場公司索償 但呢部分唔關個客事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>但我地可以睇下一個未必受保既例子</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n水浸橋龍珠島變孤島　居民玩命揸車「渡海」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/mobile/bkn-20170823170541611-0823_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170823%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170823170541611-0823_00822_001.html&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=306d96f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/mobile/bkn-20170823170541611-0823_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n部分車保 八號風球或以上非必要行駛 係屬不保事項<br />\n<br />\n不過又唔好恥笑住<br />\n<br />\n如果係八號風球掛起內兩個小時係有走盞既<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：日頭黎 點會係兩個小時內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不保事項都有例外 如果司機有必要揸車<br />\n例如去醫院 或者其實佢係返屋企<br />\n<br />\n呢d情況都係受保既<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：睇佢唔似去醫院 又應該唔係返屋企 無得賠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都未必 因為其實有公司都無呢個八號風球既不保事項 所以唔好笑咁大力住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">家居保/業主保-紅磡吊船流星錘</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">家居保會保障屋企入面既財物既損失，包括一般既財物，裝修，牆紙，地板等等<br />\n<br />\n水浸浸爛又好 流星錘扑爛都好 其實都係受保</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但留意其實有d家居保會將發展商/前業主整既裝修放係不保事項 （因為唔屬於而家業主俾錢既財產，通常因為保費平）<br />\n<br />\n咁如果係咁就唔賠個部份裝修<br />\n<br />\n姐係如果流星錘打爛既係上一手業主/發展商送既都無得賠［sosad]<br />\n<br />\n不過業主可以告間吊船既公司 而吊船公司如果有責任保險 又會係保險公司賠啦 <br />\n<br />\n仲可能會賠唔少錢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旅遊保-航班問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題我諗去開旅行都唔會陌生，不過呢個問題大家可以睇返我之前開既post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/257722/page/21?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/257722/page/21?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇份保單保咩先 唔保都無辦法<br />\n<br />\n以下正常程序<br />\n<br />\nDelay/Cancel➡問航空公司拎證明➡搞Claims➡保險公司按鐘數賠錢<br />\n<br />\nDelay/Cancel ➡問航空公司拎證明➡confirm自己份旅遊保有更改行程保障，並滿足條件➡改/買機票（留低登機證）➡如果當地有額外住宿keep埋單➡返香港Claim➡保險公司賠用左既錢<br />\n<br />\n上面兩部分通常二選一<br />\n<br />\nDelay會幫你睇埋無用到既費用 不過賠高d個邊 姐係多數會跟上面<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">個人意外 醫療保險等等</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n受傷正常程序claim就可以，但醫療要留意私家醫院會唔會有加價，個部分未必間間保險公司都賠到，最好問返自己agent<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>舖保/水險</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n會賠償貨物因水浸損失，不過我估連登應該無咩人care<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勞保</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">打風返工既朋友注意<br />\n<br />\n好多老細買勞保無包八號風球 甚至無買勞保<br />\n<br />\n如果因工受傷甚至傷亡 老細要負全責既<br />\n<br />\n有咩事受傷記得搵老細claim工傷<br />\n<br />\n如果佢無買勞保 你仲可以告佢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>商用車輛 的士 車保</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">的士車保 係唔會保八號風球下既事故</span></strong><br />\n所以任何責任 都會係的士司機負責<br />\n<br />\n呢個都係佢地話收貴大家既原因 但我個人覺得係藉口<br />\n<br />\n咁各位巴絲自己衡量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得ok既俾面like下我fb page 會update一d保險資訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/insurancebrother\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Finsurancebrother&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3601791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/insurancebrother</a>"},{"pid":"0726a5809859ca1b8e6b890e7bba80703293e31e","tid":374170,"uid":53126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a1b47c27ae1003fbbb52e7ebb1109cd9b014a3","tid":374170,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"呢d就做到野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00b0eacc92c8ec4893a212195cae25ceb9533cb","tid":374170,"uid":115451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"高質post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44c50d3445502a19196a0ebce0ad1c912e89562","tid":374170,"uid":72549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"高汁 pish"},{"pid":"38aef987373f139fa778b3dd128198a2903e38f6","tid":374170,"uid":62079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打做咩位？claims?broker?UW?"},{"pid":"f0b3d1c3f37fc9718dc5d7821e7fac1bc0bd31a1","tid":374170,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bf8c9e107dd2aa84601a41bdb0c831fd5ae10a05","tid":374170,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"保險掃盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}